A Nigerian woman has taken her chances by wooing a handsome guy on social media. The lady identified as @__Ayanfe__ on social media noticed the presence of a handsome young man and she decided to try her luck. The handsome guy shared a lovely photo of himself and Ayanfe could not resist his charm as she expressed interest in meeting him and even offering him a special #blackfriday offer.. The guy had tweeted, “Forget I’m fine man” The lady then replied to his tweet, writing, “Hey boo, Black Friday at my place this Friday, come through, i have amazing offers, especially my cloths, they will be 100% off 😍” Source